<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">masonry block</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.98</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.76</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.39</measure>) damaged at the upper right and lower left corners, and along all edges.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed on the exposed face; from a composite monument, in which the inscription continued on a block to the right, and the lower parts of the letters in l.14 were cut on the block below.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.035</measure>; ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">NH</foreign>, l4, <foreign lang="grc">TH</foreign> ll. 8, 10, 11, 12. Small circles to mark abbreviations and stops.</p>
</div>
